{
 "name": "RPlog_Poisoning_Incident_Take_Two",
 "title": "Poisoning Incident: Take Two",
 "summary": "In the lobby of the recently restored Grand Palanhi Hotel, the CSA official Sean Dillon dines and converses with the bounty hunter Roark and the easygoing Alexis about reforming the entrenched, outdated CSA leadership. The cold VicePrex Piper arrives with her Espo guards and settles near the door, sipping wine and trading nods with Alexis, while the Horansi cub Kuxli pads in and the operative Jusre and others drift through the crowded lobby. As Dillon floats a Corporate Sector contract to the intrigued Roark, the gathering simmers with the intrigue and tension surrounding a second attempt at a poisoning, the players circling one another beneath a veneer of hotel hospitality.",
